name: At Home 2010 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .T10 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: T10 files contain data that is entered in official tax forms. These tax forms can be printed or filed electronically with the At Home software.
H&R Block At Home 2010 is available in Basic, Deluxe, Premium, and Premium & Business editions.

description: Tax return created with H&R Block At Home 2010 tax software; contains a U.S. federal tax return for the 2010 tax year; may also include an individual state return if the user downloaded an At Home state edition.
